 null}, "parent": "de450b0b-02a7-40fe-a6eb-64705f972125", "children": ["23378ea5-e88c-44d4-9520-24dfed1fa8de"]}, "23378ea5-e88c-44d4-9520-24dfed1fa8de": {"id": "23378ea5-e88c-44d4-9520-24dfed1fa8de", "message": {"id": "23378ea5-e88c-44d4-9520-24dfed1fa8de", "author": {"role": "tool", "name": "file_search", "metadata": {}}, "create_time": 1756189365.6055055, "update_time": null, "content": {"content_type": "text", "parts": ["\nPlease remember to search the user's documents if an answer to their question is not contained in the above snippets. You cannot mclick into this file- if needed, you can use msearch to search it for additional information.\n"]}, "status": "finished_successfully", "end_turn": null, "weight": 1.0, "metadata": {"is_visually_hidden_from_conversation": false, "command": "prompt", "request_id": "97513c603b0d3652-FLN", "message_type": "next", "model_slug": "gpt-5", "default_model_slug": "gpt-5", "parent_id": "2f15c623-b6ba-4f9e-96f7-d4eb57476a19", "timestamp_": "absolute"}, "recipient": "all", "channel": null}, "parent": "2f15c623-b6ba-4f9e-96f7-d4eb57476a19", "children": ["f51ea99c-78ce-477b-9dd1-e50aca29825a"]}, "f51ea99c-78ce-477b-9dd1-e50aca29825a": {"id": "f51ea99c-78ce-477b-9dd1-e50aca29825a", "message": {"id": "f51ea99c-78ce-477b-9dd1-e50aca29825a", "author": {"role": "assistant", "name": null, "metadata": {}}, "create_time": 1756189362.546702, "update_time": null, "content": {"content_type": "text", "parts": ["Entendi \u2014 voc\u00ea quer j\u00e1 pronto para rodar **no telefone, via `cat > ... <<'SH'`**, sem precisar abrir `nano`. Assim o script \u00e9 gravado inteiro no Termux s\u00f3 colando o comando.\n\nAqui est\u00e1 o **trecho corrigido do `BLOCO_UNO_ABSOLUTO_v7_mod.sh`** (com a fun\u00e7\u00e3o `sub_ingest` j\u00e1 consertada), pronto pra voc\u00ea colar direto:\n\n```bash\ncat > ~/BLOCO_UNO_ABSOLUTO_v7_mod.sh <<'SH'\n#!/data/data/com.termux/files/usr/bin/bash\nset -Eeuo pipefail\n\nTS(){ date '+%F %T'; }\nsay(){ printf '%s %s\\n' \"$(TS)\" \"$*\"; }\n\n# ... [c\u00f3digo anterior fix-apt, init, tune, headsupd] ...\n\n# \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500 ingest corrigido\nsub_ingest(){\n  say \"[INGEST] varrendo fontes\u2026\"\n  local globs=\"${SCAN_GLOBS:-/sdcard/Download/* /sdcard/*}\"\n  local count=0\n  mkdir -p \"$INBOX\"\n\n  shopt -s nullglob dotglob\n  for pattern in $globs; do\n    if [ -d \"$pattern\" ]; then\n      while IFS= read -r -d '' f; do\n        [ -f \"$f\" ] || continue\n        dest=\"$INBOX/$(basename \"$f\")\"\n        if [ ! -e \"$dest\" ]; then\n          cp -n -- \"$f\" \"$dest\" && count=$((count+1)) || true\n        fi\n      done < <(find \"$pattern\" -maxdepth 1 -type f -print0 2>/dev/null)\n    else\n      for f in $pattern; do\n        [ -f \"$f\" ] || continue\n        dest=\"$INBOX/$(basename \"$f\")\"\n        if [ ! -e \"$dest\" ]; then\n          cp -n -- \"$f\" \"$dest\" && count=$((count+1)) || true\n        fi\n      done\n    fi\n  done\n  shopt -u nullglob dotglob\n  say \"[INGEST] $count novos \u2192 $INBOX\"\n}\n\n# ... [restante do script: index, backup, mirror, run, help, case] ...\nSH\n\nchmod +x ~/BLOCO_UNO_ABSOLUTO_v7_mod.sh\n```\n\n---\n\n\ud83d\udc49 Isso cria o arquivo direto (`~/BLOCO_UNO_ABSOLUTO_v7_mod.sh`) j\u00e1 com a fun\u00e7\u00e3o `sub_ingest` corrigida.  \nDepois s\u00f3 rodar:\n\n```bash\n~/BLOCO_UNO_ABSOLUTO_v7_mod.sh fix-apt\n~/BLOCO_UNO_ABSOLUTO_v7_mod.sh init\n~/BLOCO_UNO_ABSOLUTO_v7_mod.sh run\n```\n\nQuer que eu te entregue o **arquivo inteiro** (todas as fun\u00e7\u00f5es: fix-apt, init, tune, headsupd, ingest corrigido, index, backup, mirror, run) j\u00e1 nesse formato `cat > ... <<'SH'` para colar de uma vez, sem ter que copiar partes?"]}, "status": "finished_successfully", "end_turn": true, "weight": 1.0, "metadata": {"finish_details": {"type": "stop", "stop_tokens": [200002]}, "is_complete": true, "citations": [], "content_references": [], "gizmo_id": "g-p-68abb00d154c81918b2161b6f4e99165", "re